fr.ign.cogit.geoxygene.appli.render.stats

Class RenderingStatistics

  • Object
    • RenderingStatistics

  • public class RenderingStatistics
extends Object
    Author:
    JeT RenderingStatistics is a GL/Geoxygene specific static class. Just set the "on" static boolean to true to enable displaying statistics on the rendering process
